      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "12778-12838",
      "markText": "简说这些猫肯定不对头，话说回来，我很可能这辈子都不再跟她讲话。她连猫的闲话都要说，我这辈子就是忍受不了别人暗地里说闲话。",
      "totalCount": 1139,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021854&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=12778&rangeEnd=12838",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da32f60813ab6f09g014c5c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=12778&rangeEnd=12838"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300021854_17_14589-14658",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "14589-14658",
      "markText": "“路易莎，”她说，“回家吧。我们都想我们亲爱的孩子回来，我们需要你，我们很想你。你的妈妈、爸爸爱你，而且永远不会忘记你。回家吧，路易莎。”",
      "totalCount": 1022,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300021854&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=14589&rangeEnd=14658",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/0da32f60813ab6f09g014c5c?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=14589&rangeEnd=14658"
    },
    {
